metadata.name: Voxel Tanukichi
metadata.description: One woman rides a blue bird and someday she will be flying over Japan and across the great ocean.We are encouraged by the sight of her riding in a yukata against the world.Because it is a person who has a stronger will than anyone else, and who thinks for the sake of others more than anyone else.But just for today, it is for you.Happy birthday, Tanukichi. From my heart, for you VEN
